src.list

Class ArrayList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.list.List<E>
      • src.list.ArrayList<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>, iList<E>

    public class ArrayList<E>
extends List<E>
    List implementation using a resizable array. Array will expand when there is no extra space. Expansion will incur a performance penalty, hence chosing the correct base size is a good idea.
    Since:
    v1.0
